---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Kuzupost PhotoStrips - Support">
    <div
        class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6 min-h-[60vh] flex flex-col items-center mt-10"
    >
        <div
            class="bg-neo-white border-4 border-neo-black neo-shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12 w-full"
        >
            <h1
                class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-neo-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-8 bg-neo-cyan inline-block px-4 py-2 border-4 border-neo-black neo-shadow transform -rotate-1"
            >
                Support
            </h1>

            <div
                class="space-y-6 text-lg font-medium leading-relaxed text-neo-black mt-6"
            >
                <p class="bg-neo-pink/30 p-4 border-l-4 border-neo-black">
                    Need help? We're here for you. Whether you're experiencing
                    issues with the photo booth, have questions about your saved
                    photos, or just want to leave feedback, don't hesitate to
                    reach out!
                </p>

                <div
                    class="bg-neo-yellow/30 p-6 border-4 border-neo-black neo-shadow mt-8"
                >
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
                        Frequently Asked Questions
                    </h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="border-b-2 border-neo-black pb-2">
                            <h3 class="font-bold">
                                Q: Mengapa kamera saya tidak berfungsi?
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-sm mt-1">
                                A: Pastikan Anda memberikan izin akses kamera ke
                                browser. Muat ulang halaman dan klik "Allow"
                                saat diminta.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="border-b-2 border-neo-black pb-2">
                            <h3 class="font-bold">
                                Q: Di mana foto saya disimpan?
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-sm mt-1">
                                A: Foto-foto diunduh secara lokal ke perangkat
                                Anda. Kami tidak menyimpan foto di server mana
                                pun demi privasi Anda.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold">
                                Q: Apakah aplikasi ini gratis?
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-sm mt-1">
                                A: Ya! Semua fitur gratis untuk digunakan.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-12 text-center md:text-left">
                <button
                    onclick="window.history.back();"
                    class="neo-button bg-neo-yellow rounded-none border-4"
                >
                    <i class="fa fa-arrow-left mr-2"></i> Kembali
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
